  "original_title": "\u0b87\u0bb2\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b87\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1 \u0bae\u0bc7\u0bb2\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd 7 \u0baa\u0bc7\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bae\u0bbf\u0bb4\u0b95\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0b9e\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "7 more people from Sri Lanka have taken refuge in Tamil Nadu",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "Due to the economic problem in the country, illegal migration from Sri Lanka to Tamil Nadu continues.",
        "In this case, 2 families from Sri Lanka have gone to Dhanushkodi in Tamil Nadu as refugees amid strong winds and rough seas.",
        "Yesterday Friday at 06.00 pm, the Indian Coast Guard saw 7 Sri Lankan refugees drowning on the 1st sandbar in the middle of the sea near Dhanushkodi.",
        "They continued to go there and rescued 7 refugees including 3 children, put them on board and gave them food and took them to Arichalmunya beach last night.",
        "Vigneswaran (40) from Vavuniya Chettikulam area, Sri Lanka, his wife Rajakumari (36) and sons Kumaran (13), Vasi (10) and Kumaran (38) from the same area, his wife Madini (30) and son Pavin (6) from the same area. ) was also revealed.",
        "Due to the economic crisis in Sri Lanka, 104 people have gone to Tamil Nadu as refugees so far."
      ],
